Author: Rickticia
Text: I’m sorry. It really sucks that you were brave enough to seek help and they couldn’t offer more support realistic with where you are college wise. Are there any other groups you could go for some kind of support?

Author: _Fr0gg0_
Text: Well shit... I'm sorta in the same position. Restricting under their calorie mark and my thearpist just referred me out to an ED clinic... I'm college age but work full time.  I'm supposed to get a call from the clinic soon to set up the initial appointment.  Best of luck! Let me know what you choose to do!
